T02D1949:75b-1: danda dhrik bi d'a ra ya m'a ri s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02D1949:75b-3: dbyug pa gshin rje gshed rnam par 'joms pa zhes bya ba'i sgrub thabs /
T02D1949:75b-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1949:75b-5: thugs kyi de nyid gtso dang mtshungs pa yi //
T02D1949:75b-6: lha ni bdud dgra dbyug pa gshin rje gshed //
T02D1949:75b-7: las rnams thams cad mthar mdzed la btung te //
T02D1949:75b-8: mchog gi dngos grub bsgrub phyir bshad par bya /
T02D1949:75b-10: // rang lus phyag rgya chen por dran //
T02D1949:75b-11: theg pa chen po'i blor byas nas //
T02D1949:75b-12: bla ma rje btsun rnams la ni //
T02D1949:75b-13: bsod nams tshogs rab bsag par bya //
T02D1949:75b-14: gnyis med sangs rgyas gnyis su med //
T02D1949:75b-15: rkyen skyes chogs kun chu zla 'dra //
T02D1949:75b-16: de nyid skye med shes bya'i phyir //
T02D1949:75b-17: dag pa'i sngags kyis bskul la bsgom //
T02D1949:75b-18: chad med rgyun chad med pa'i sems //
T02D1949:75b-19: nam mkha'i thigs pa de nyid las //
T02D1949:75b-20: srung ba'i 'khor lo gdan bsams te //
T02D1949:75b-21: dza las dbyug pa dkar dang //
T02D1949:75b-23: rtsa zhal dkar la sngo dmar zhal //
T02D1949:75b-24: rang gi rig mar mtshungs pa'i lus //
T02D1949:75b-25: gri gug dbyug pa ral gri dang //
T02D1949:76a-0: @76a * // g-yas bskum g-yon brkyang ba yi zhabs //
T02D1949:76a-1: chu skyes 'od zer rnon po mnan //
T02D1949:76a-2: mi mgo'i phreng dpyangs stag lpags mnabs //
T02D1949:76a-3: klu dang rus rgyan dbus mdzes pa //
T02D1949:76a-4: bskyed la lus ngag yid gsum dang //
T02D1949:76a-5: skye mched rnams la 'dis byin brlab //
T02D1949:76a-7: kshim jim kham gam kam sam //
T02D1949:76a-8: dbang bskur cod pan mi bskyod bsam /
T02D1949:76a-9: dza: h'um bam ho: sa byin gyis brlab //
T02D1949:76a-10: byang chub sems kyi sprul pas mchod //
T02D1949:76a-11: de nas rdo rje dril ldan pas //
T02D1949:76a-12: bstod pa'i rgyal po brjod par bya //
T02D1949:76a-13: sangs rgyas rdo rje kun du bzang //
T02D1949:76a-14: mnyam pa'i rdo rje mi bskyod pa //
T02D1949:76a-15: rdo rje gsang ba dbyings chen po //
T02D1949:76a-16: ye shes rdo rje phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D1949:76a-17: yig 'bru gsum gyis byin brlabs pa'i //
T02D1949:76a-18: bdud rtsi rdo rje lce yis myang //
T02D1949:76a-19: spro dang bsdu ba byas nas kyang //
T02D1949:76a-20: gsang sngags khri ru bzlas pa bya //
T02D1949:76a-21: aom badzra danda dhrik h'um h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02D1949:76a-22: sa chu me rlung 'byung ba'i rim //
T02D1949:76a-23: ye shes thig ler byas nas kyang//
T02D1949:76a-24: gzugs ni sgra nyid rang bzhin dag / bdag med snying po bsgom par bya //
T02D1949:76a-25: ma rig mun pa 'joms byed sgron ma'i mchog / bdud dgra khro bo'i rgyal po'i sgrub thabs 'dis //
T02D1949:76a-26: 'gro ba'i 'jigs chen nges dgra bcom nas kyang //
T02D1949:76a-27: thams cad gshin rje gshed po nyid mtshungs shog /
T02D1949:76a-28: dbyug pa gshin rje gshed rnam par 'joms pa zhes
T02D1949:76a-30: slob dpon chen po d'i pam ka ras mdzad pa rdzogs so /
